# CERR Mahalla Analytics — 1.4 GB scraped JSON tree.
# Source data lives outside git (R2 bucket nbu-cerr-data, served at
# https://cerr-data.devgokal.com). Path is configurable via CERR_DATA_ROOT.
# The legacy Flask + Next.js iframe wrapper that used to live at
# region_analytics_platform_template/platform/ is gone — the cerr-v2
# native Vue port replaced it.
region_analytics_platform_template/cerr_runs/

# chatbot service ships docker image tarballs from the colleague (~225 MB total).
